OL,6,FDevon and Cornwall Police has been
OL,7,Faccused of "systemic failures" in the
OL,8,Finvestigation of alleged domestic
OL,9,Fabuse by its own officers.
OL,11,FThe Centre for Women's Justice (CWJ)
OL,12,Fis suing the force at the High Court,
OL,13,Fon behalf of seven women whose human
OL,14,Frights were allegedly breached.
