OL,3,CPolice force accused of failing to
OL,4,Cinvestigate reports of domestic abuse
OL,6,FAccording to the CWJ, its seven,
OL,7,Funrelated, reports of police
OL,8,Fperpetrated domestic abuse (PPDA) were
OL,9,Fso badly handled that they show there
OL,10,Fis a systemic failure by Devon and
OL,11,FCornwall Police to investigate these
OL,12,Fcrimes.
OL,14,F'Lizzie', not her real name, is one of
OL,15,Fthe seven women involved in the claim.
