OL,3,CPolice force accused of failing to
OL,4,Cinvestigate reports of domestic abuse
OL,6,FShe said: "I have lost all faith in
OL,7,FD&C police. It's quite a terrifying
OL,8,Fexperience knowing that every single
OL,9,Fofficer I have dealt with over the
OL,10,Fyears will prioritise protecting a
OL,11,Ffellow officer rather than
OL,12,Finvestigating a report of abuse.
OL,14,F"If I can help to ensure that no other
OL,15,Fwoman is made to feel as vulnerable
OL,16,Fand hopeless as I have been left
OL,17,Ffeeling by D&C police, then this
OL,18,Faction will have been a success."
