OL,6,FThe CWJ said it was approached by the
OL,7,Fwomen individually, most following the
OL,8,Fpublication of its into how all
OL,9,Fforces, nationally, are failing to
OL,10,Faddress PPDA.
OL,12,FIt added that they reported a range of
OL,13,Fabuse by their then-police officer
OL,14,Fpartners, including rape, physical and
OL,15,Fmental abuse, coercive and controlling
OL,16,Fbehaviour, harassment and stalking.
