OL,3,CPolice force accused of failing to
OL,4,Cinvestigate reports of domestic abuse
OL,6,FAccording to the CWJ, Devon and
OL,7,FCornwall Police failed to take basic
OL,8,Finvestigative steps and in one case,
OL,9,Feven treated the victim - herself a
OL,10,Fformer police officer - as a potential
OL,11,Foffender based on counter-allegations
OL,12,Fraised by her perpetrator which were
OL,13,Flater found to be false.
OL,15,F'Samantha', not her real name, who is
OL,16,Falso involved in the claim, said: "I
OL,17,Fhave gone from trusting the police to
OL,18,Fno longer being able to trust them or
OL,19,Fothers.
