OL,3,CPolice force accused of failing to
OL,4,Cinvestigate reports of domestic abuse
OL,6,F"Coming together with the Centre for
OL,7,FWomen's Justice and other women who
OL,8,Fhave experienced similar at the hands
OL,9,Fof D&C police has been the only hope I
OL,10,Fhave had over the last few years.
OL,12,F"If I had to start over, I would never
OL,13,Freport to the police as the process
OL,14,Fand their handling was just as bad as
OL,15,Fthe abuser and the abuse prior to
OL,16,Freporting. I want to have my voice
OL,17,Fheard so others don't have to endure
OL,18,Fwhat I have and still go through."
