OL,6,FThe CWJ claims other failings by the
OL,7,Fforce include appointing investigators
OL,8,Fconnected to the accused officers and
OL,9,Ffailing to gather statements from
OL,10,Fpotential witnesses.
OL,12,FIt added that it believes there was a
OL,13,Fwholesale failure to update the women,
OL,14,Fclaiming - "some of (them) remain in
OL,15,Fthe dark as to what, if any,
OL,16,Finvestigation has been conducted".
