OL,4,Cinvestigate reports of domestic abuse
OL,6,FDebaleena Dasgupta, a solicitor at CWJ
OL,7,Fwho is acting in the claim, said: "The
OL,8,Fwomen's combined testimonies paint a
OL,9,Fpicture of a force not just unable to
OL,10,Finvestigate police perpetrated
OL,11,Fdomestic abuse, but seemingly
OL,12,Funwilling to.
OL,14,F"This case shows that in multiple,
OL,15,Funrelated, matters, D&C have failed to
OL,16,Ftake even basic steps to investigate
OL,17,Ftheir own officers who have been
OL,18,Faccused of serious domestic abuse.
