OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F439A1707926895
OL,3,CPolice force accused of failing to
OL,4,Cinvestigate reports of domestic abuse
OL,6,F"Some of the accused officers remain
OL,7,Fin D&C, including in roles which are
OL,8,Fmeant to address violence against
OL,9,Fwomen and girls in the area. Not one
OL,10,Fofficer was even properly investigated
OL,11,Ffor misconduct, let alone for criminal
OL,12,Foffences. What does this tell us about
OL,13,Fvetting in the force?
OL,15,F"Without exception, the women bringing
OL,16,Fthis case have explained that they
OL,17,Fhave lost faith in D&C. Some say they
OL,18,Fwished they had never reported at all,
OL,19,Fgiven the way they have been treated.
