OL,3,CPolice force accused of failing to
OL,4,Cinvestigate reports of domestic abuse
OL,6,F"As part of their claim, the women
OL,7,Fhave offered to help D&C improve its
OL,8,Fpractices and procedures. It is up to
OL,9,FD&C how they intend to address this.
OL,10,FIt is my clients' hope that D&C will
OL,11,Frecognise that they have failed, and
OL,12,Ftry to put this right for others."
OL,14,FIn response to the claim being brought
OL,15,Fagainst the force, Assistant Chief
OL,16,FConstable Jim Pearce said: "Devon &
OL,17,FCornwall Police has been made aware of
OL,18,Finformation received on 2 February
OL,19,F2024 which requires careful
OL,20,Fconsideration and appropriate review.
