OL,6,F"As a result of the information
OL,7,Freceived, the Force has made a
OL,8,Fmandatory referral to the Independent
OL,9,FOffice for Police Conduct (IOPC).
OL,11,F"The IOPC has asked for further work
OL,12,Fto be progressed by the Force before
OL,13,Fthey can accept and assess a referral,
OL,14,Fbut we remain in consultation with
OL,15,Fthem in providing the required
OL,16,Finformation.
OL,18,F"It would be both inappropriate and
OL,19,Fpremature to comment further at this
OL,20,Fstage."
